            "SummaryExplanation": {
                "val": "FY2018: $8.433M increase to meet USSTRATCOM-led Joint Space Doctrine and Tactics Forum requirement to develop more accurate modeling and analytical tools for depicting space contributions across all phases of conflict.  Funds subject matter expertise to develop space modeling, simulation and analysis tools at the engagement, mission and campaign levels for 15 different warfighter mission areas."
            }
